snippet.title: Sketchy's Contract EA Trailer
snippet.description:
#horrorgaming #earlyaccessgames #videogames Sketchy's Contract is an upcoming co-op sci-fi horror game where players travel to exotic planets to farm minerals, kill creatures, and/or find hidden loot that can be brought to an asteroid belt and turned in for rewards.

Wishlist NOW on steam!
